Flags:

CFLAGS - Captures the difference between debug, optimized, profile compiles

Set:

debug.make, optimized.make, profiled.make

Used:

to set CFLAGSnog (debug.make)
to define COMPILE.gnu.[osi] (link.make)
to define COMPILE.gnu.precomp (mac_osx,linux).make


CFLAGSnog: has g if debug, no if not debug

Used:

to set COMPILE.gnu.o.nog, which is used for compiling glue

GNUFLAGS

Set:

lots of gcc flags (link.make)

GNUOPTFLAGS -- GNU optimized flags

Set:

Used:

LDFLAGS

Set:

Used:

GLUE_LD_FLAGS


